flowchart TD
    C[Client / Postman / Mobile App] --> AG[API Gateway / JWT Auth]
    AG --> API[KYC API - Go]
    API -->|202 transaction_id| C
    API -->|encrypted job event| K[(Kafka-compatible Redpanda Topics\nkyc_enroll / kyc_verify)]
    W[KYC Worker - Go] -->|poll jobs| K
    W --> INF[Inference Service - Python + uv\nArcFace 512D + Name 768D + Liveness]
    W --> Q[(Qdrant Vector DB\nface_embeddings / name_embeddings\nHNSW indexes)]
    W --> R[(Redis KV Metadata\nhashes / status / DID)]
    W --> CB[Optional Callback URL]
    C -->|GET /kyc/status/{transaction_id}| API
    API --> R
    API --> M[Prometheus /metrics]
    M --> G[Grafana Dashboard]
